actually titled it, Conference

00:25:48.830 --> 00:25:52.430 align:middle line:84%
on Free Energy and thought,
oh, this is a great chance

00:25:52.430 --> 00:25:53.690 align:middle line:90%
to finally bring it out.

00:25:53.690 --> 00:25:56.750 align:middle line:84%
It's been a decade,
actually two decades

00:25:56.750 --> 00:25:58.670 align:middle line:90%
