00:25:58.670 --> 00:26:00.230 align:middle line:90%
I thought the time was right.

00:26:00.230 --> 00:26:02.052 align:middle line:90%
Turns out I was totally wrong.

00:26:02.052 --> 00:26:04.010 align:middle line:84%
>>NOORY: Well, you were
right about the timing.

00:26:04.010 --> 00:26:05.468 align:middle line:84%
