were wrong, right?

00:26:05.468 --> 00:26:06.305 align:middle line:90%
>>VALONE: Exactly.

00:26:06.305 --> 00:26:06.740 align:middle line:90%
The back ledge.

00:26:06.740 --> 00:26:07.700 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: What did they do?

00:26:07.700 --> 00:26:08.570 align:middle line:90%
>>VALONE: Oh my goodness.

